what_worked: Applied decorrelate, date_cte_isolate, prefetch_fact_join achieving 11.62x speedup
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input
